.TH "LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-REMOTE-BALANCE" 1 "May 2026" "lightning 0.6.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-remote-balance \- show local and remote balance across active channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B lightning channel-remote-balance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Sums local and remote balances across all CHANNELD_NORMAL channels.
.PP
Output: JSON object with total_msat, local_msat, remote_msat, active_channels.
.SH EXIT STATUS
.TP
.B 0
Always.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR lightning-channel-local-balance (1),
.BR lightning-channel-incoming-capacity (1)
